page.title: 16HOME LIFE 2
page.content: IN THE MORNING WHEN I WAKE UP I GET DRESSED AND WASH MY FACE AND HANDS.AFTER THAT I WAKE UP MUM AND GO DOWN THE STAIRS.WHEN MY MUM GETS UP SHE COMES DOWN STAIRS.I HAVE EGG,BACON AND BLACK PUDDING FOR BREAKFAST.AFTER THAT I BRUSH MY TEETH AND GO TO SCHOOL. WHEN I GET THERE,I PLAY FOOTBALL UNTIL WHISTLE.WHEN I GO IN,I WRITE A STORY AND DO SUMS UNTIL PLAYTIME.WHEN PLAYTIME COMES WE PLAY FOOTBALL.WHEN WE GO IN,WE FINISH OUR SUMS.WHEN IT IS LUNCHTIME,I SOMETIMES STAY FOR SCHOOL DINNERS.AFTER THAT MORE WRITING THEN ANOTHER PLAYTIME.WE GET GYM ON TUESDAYS.THEN WE READ A BOOK UNTIL IT IS TIME TO GO HOME.
